 arch/arm64/boot/dts/cix/sky1-orion-o6n.dts | 66 +---------------------
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/cix/sky1.dtsi          | 25 ++++----
 3 files changed, 13 insertions(+), 82 deletions(-)

